casebody.data:
Eric DETEL, Appellant,
v.
DIVISION OF EMPLOYMENT SECURITY, Respondent. WD 80902 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: September 4, 2018 Eric Detel, Appellant Pro Se. Bart A. Matanic, Jefferson City, MO, for respondent. Before Division Four: Karen King Mitchell, Chief Judge, Presiding, Mark D. Pfeiffer, Judge and Cynthia L. Martin, Judge

ORDER

Per curiam:

Eric Detel appeals from the Labor and Industrial Relations Commission's decision that concluded Detel was ineligible for unemployment benefits because he left work voluntarily but not for good cause attributable to the work or his employer. We affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
